NAME
    Spark - A simple yet powerful forms validation system that promotes
    reuse.

VERSION
    version 0.1.0

DESCRIPTION
    At this time, most of the documentation for this module is in
    Spark::Form, and this module ( Spark ) is merely a placeholder.

